Summary: i have been getting picts and video for a few weeks over the northern P.A. area,these are right my front door
divs: Sighting Detailsfor the last few weeks i have been watching these strange lights in the sky .so one day i opened my front door at around 7 o'clock p.m.and right up above the tree line there they where just hovering. Does the gov.send out drones just to watch it's citizens.
